    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014garage-kept, smoke-free, and not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car vibe. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it just as much. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
