    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 1997 BMW M3 Coupe, finished in Alpine White over Magma Nappa leather. This example retains its numbers-matching S52 3.2L DOHC 24-valve inline-six, featuring a meticulously maintained variable valve timing (VANOS) system and a flawless ZF 5-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the chassis features a reinforced rear subframe, Bilstein B6 dampers, and fresh polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection. Power is delivered through a factory 3.15-ratio limited-slip differential. The exterior boasts original paint depth across all panels with zero oxidation, while the forged Style 24 'Lightweight' wheels remain free of curb rash. This is a turn-key, investment-quality E36 with zero deferred maintenance and a comprehensive service history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
